            that the TNBS works perfectly under flat yield curves. In that situation, any bond can be delivered without any loss. In this section, I suggest some extensions that could be used to fine‐tune the TNBS. Their purpose is to deal better with nonflat yield curves while keeping the futures invoice price as a function of only
